fulltitle: Branford Marsalis: Conversations with Doctor Thunder (Ep. 62)
description:
#Conversations #BranfordMarsalis #Saxophone

Conversations with Doctor Thunder is a series of interviews with musicians, artists, dancers, pastors, philanthropists, motivational speakers, entrepreneurs, politicians, academics, athletes and etc. Today's interview is with Saxophone icon; Branford Marsalis. Learn more about him here https://www.branfordmarsalis.com/. Enjoy! 

Table of Contents:
0:00 Intro
4:00 Classical saxophone and Challenging Yourself

46:00 Accessibility Of Music and Spirituality
50:30 The Master And Apprentice, Music In Church
1:00:00 Branford's Setup
